  <string key="T2000046" eng="This sword is filled with the power of the spirit dragon. Made of wood, the sword and its wielder are connected closely to nature. Once carried by the shamans of the NetSphere, it brought their enemies down like rain. The Dragon might fulfill the wishes of its owner if your belief is strong enough.{N}" />
  <string key="T2000047" eng="This sword is filled with the power of the spirit dragon. Made of wood, the sword and its wielder are closely connected to nature. Once carried by the shamans of the NetSphere, it brought their enemies down like rain. The Dragon might fulfill the wishes of its owner if your belief is strong enough.{N}" />
  <string key="T2000048" eng="A unique Plasma Sword, it's been painted a gleaming gold and decorated with sturdy chains." />
  <string key="T2000049" />
  <string key="T2000050" />
  <string key="T2000051" eng="Unique counter sword decorated with extravagant chains and spikes." />
  <string key="T2000052" />
  <string key="T2000053" />
  <string key="T2000054" eng="Ein Replika von no.6 Lockes Katana Deleter.{N} Durch die schmale Schwertscheide und den kurzen Griff werden zwar Abstriche in Sachen Sicherheit gemacht, dafür bist du mit diesem Katana umso schneller und tödlicher." />
  <string key="T2000055" eng="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Counter Sword.{N}This unique weapon was developed during Luna's test phase.{N}With the ability to switch freely between offensive and defensive modes, it's an extremely effective and flexible weapon.{N}Winner of the EU Community Workshop contest: Krayds" />
  <string key="T2000056" eng="Bloody Hunter and Bloody Huntress's Unique EXO Scythe.{N}Its shape is reminiscent of dripping blood,{N}It is said to have a thirst for blood, but this appears to be merely apocryphal.{N}Its full name is the &quot;Thanatos of Death&quot; Scythe." />
  <string key="T2000057" eng="A weapon created when Glitch was born.{N}Nobody knows the true source of this black-and-white dual blade that annihilates data and tears through code." />
  <string key="T2000058" eng="Glitch's White Twin Blade. {N}The seal was broken by the outbreak of Dead Pixel, and its true power was released." />
  <string key="T2000059" eng="Destruction Glitch's unique spy dagger.{N}A shadowy variant of Glitch's Twin Blade. This weapon's devastating black blade is comprised of indecipherable, malicious code." />
  <string key="T2000060" />
  <string key="T2000061" />
  <string key="T2000062" />
  <string key="T2000063" eng="This lethal melee weapon was sealed deep inside the Netsphere.{N}A prototype version was uncovered, and the Netsphere developer, Uz, was able to redesign and upgrade it with help of Mr. J and Mr. B. " />
  <string key="T2000064" eng="Curiosity killed the cat, huh? Well, these claws are just as deadly!{N}If you're looking for a great new way to shred your foes to ribbons, look no further. These claws will earn you applause!" />
  <string key="T2000065" eng="A unique Leo Vital Shock.{N}Based on a stolen prototype of an unknown creator,{N}this Vital Shock is modeled after deadly feline claws. " />
  <string key="T2000066" />
  <string key="T2000067" eng="A bayonet symbolizing the arrogance of the corrupted ones.  Though dark, it gives off a powerful energy." />
  <string key="T2000068" eng="A bayonet symbolizing the arrogance of the corrupted ones. Though dark, it gives off a powerful energy." />
  <string key="T2000069" />
  <string key="T2000070" />
  <string key="T2000071" eng="A bat shaped like a firework, complete with burning wick.{N} Though it looks ready to blast off into the summer night, its wick is only for decoration." />
  <string key="T2000072" eng="This upgraded version of the katana was stolen by Hacker G.{N}Originally, various versions of the katana were being developed in tandem with the Sigma Blade. However, research was halted due to the unexpected Hacker G attack. As a result, only a bare-bones, slashing katana was available... until now." />
  <string key="T2000073" eng="This upgraded version of the katana was stolen by Hacker G.{N}Originally, various versions of the katana were being developed in tandem with the Sigma Blade. However, research was halted due to the unexpected Hacker G attack. As a result, only a bare-bones, slashing katana was available... until now." />
  <string key="T2000074" eng="This plasma sword was customized to meet riders' demanding expectations. {N}A redesigned plasma dismantler was utilized to enhance stability and portability." />
  <string key="T2000075" eng="Popular among up-and-coming rock stars, this hardcore guitar easily shreds enemies using acute sonic distortions.{N}Outside of battle, it transports its avid listeners to new and exciting soundscapes." />
  <string key="T2000076" eng="This custom counter sword is modeled after a Christmas wreath." />
  <string key="T2000077" eng="A deadly weapon that freezes the wounds of your enemies to inflict additional pain." />
  <string key="T2000078" eng="These fan-shaped weapons are as beautiful as they are dangerous. Use with caution." />
  <string key="T2000079" eng="It's a special breaker to &quot;fix&quot; damaged code when their glitched nemesis needs a &quot;forced reprogramming&quot;.{N}For those agents preferring to work undetected, this breaker is used for emergencies only." />
  <string key="T2000080" eng="The oak tree wood makes it hard to break, {N} and the best part is that the fish was recently caught and is still fresh." />
  <string key="T2000081" eng="Tactical Knife is a multi-functional knife with a sharp blade that will inflict deadly damage on any enemy within range." />
  <string key="T2000082" eng="An Arctic Surprise that commemorates Christmas.{N}I do not know what is in it, but it is certainly not a good gift.{N}Please note that you may get hurt when opening this gift." />
  <string key="T2000083" eng="Gold edition of the Tactical Knife. Its most stunning feature is the bling-bling gold covered exterior." />
  <string key="T2000084" eng="An airplane-shaped shield made of 8-bit pixels with a rainbow glow. The Galaxy Counter Sword can defeat the enemy's attack with the energy of the Galaxy!" />
  <string key="T2000085" eng="This Golden Dragon Scythe was made by a blacksmith blessed by the heavens. The Scythe is emanating a powerful red energy. &quot;If you are the true master of the Golden Dragon Scythe, you'll be able to hear the voice of the dragon.&quot;" />
  <string key="T2000086" eng="Coded into the Netsphere by an unknown entity, this hammer is perfect for broken-hearted lovers to take revenge and look good at the same time." />
  <string key="T2000088" eng="You can cut through EVERYTHING!" />
  <string key="T2000089" eng="Prototype Twinblades from Project Zin!" />
  <string key="T2000090" eng="This will split your enemy in half!" />
  <string key="T2000091" eng="This is a long Razorblade!" />
  <string key="T2000092" eng="The Frequency changes when you hit faster!" />
  <string key="T2000093" eng="8-Bit Sword from a strange Arcade Game" />
  <string key="T2000094" eng="Get back in the kitchen!" />
  <string key="T2000101" eng="This legendary Sword finally got free out of the stone with all it's Power!" />
  <string key="T2000104" eng="Monk used this Katana to fight new {N}S4League Players!" />
  <string key="T2000108" eng="Made for children but then official never released!" />
  <string key="T2000112" eng="This Sword is made by Lgndz! {N}Since he disappeared, it has become weaker!" />
  <string key="T2000115" eng="Created by Matty!" />
  <string key="T2000117" eng="Dr.Icey created this special Knife!" />
  <string key="T2000118" eng="Failed experiment. It's unstable, look out!" />
  <string key="T2000120" eng="Iron forged Knife!" />
  <string key="T2000121" eng="Detailed Scythe! It will cost a Fortune!" />
  <string key="T2000122" eng="The small blades where one big blade once... but what happend?" />
  <string key="T2000123" eng="The inside of this sword is empty to force more energy to flow" />
  <string key="T2000124" eng="Kill Psyclope X to get random Bloody or if you lucky to find a Red Meteonyker flying around." />
  <string key="T2000125" eng="Revenge yourself with this sword!" />
  <string key="T2000126" eng="Escanors Axe! Run when you see it!" />
  <string key="T2000133" eng="Festival of five petal flowers and sign of cherry blossoms that are symbolic flowers of spring, a time of renewal, and the fleeting nature of life. Their life is very short. After their beauty peaks around two weeks, the blossoms start to fall." />
  <string key="T2000134" eng="This Dagger was made in the early days of S4League!" />
  <string key="T2000135" eng="This was Asuna's Rapier. Somehow it managed to make it into the Netsphere of S4 League." />
  <string key="T2000136" eng="This was Kirito's one-handed Sword. Somehow it managed to make it into the Netsphere of S4 League." />
  <string key="T2000137" eng="Festival of five petal flowers and sign of cherry blossoms that are symbolic flowers of spring, a time of renewal, and the fleeting nature of life. Their life is very short. After their beauty peaks around two weeks, the blossoms start to fall." />
  <string key="T2000138" eng="Festival of five petal flowers and sign of cherry blossoms that are symbolic flowers of spring, a time of renewal, and the fleeting nature of life. Their life is very short. After their beauty peaks around two weeks, the blossoms start to fall." />
  <string key="T2000139" eng="A Plasma Sword colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2000140" eng="A Counter Sword colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2000141" eng="A Gate Breaker colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2000142" eng="Attack with the power of the Aqua super nova!" />
  <string key="T2000143" eng="Parry with the power of thousands of stars!" />
  <string key="T2000144" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2000145" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2000146" eng="Some left over candy while celebrating christmas." />
  <string key="T2000147" eng="With the honey of the bee's we were able to craft this weapon.{N}Warning! It's sticky!" />
  <string key="T2000148" eng="Someone stole a Pumpkin from a Halloween Party and made a weapon out of it." />
  <string key="T2000149" eng="A weeb has collected multiple waifu-sheets and pulled them over a Plasma Sword." />
  <string key="T2000150" eng="Only the Hero of Hyrule is able to wear this legendary Master Sword and Shield.{N}Are you the one?" />
  <string key="T2000185" eng="" />
  <string key="T2010009" eng="Blue fish Sub Machine Gun{N}containing plenty of DHA and Omega 3{N}(We cannot guarantee nutrition.)" />
  <string key="T2010010" eng="Faked cute look.{N}Puppy revolver with strong fire power." />
  <string key="T2010011" eng="You will be seized with fear by just looking at it, and you will get severe pain when you are shot. Ouch!! !" />
  <string key="T2010012" eng="Put together two things everybody likes. Cat and Laser!! Who will be the winner of Laser Cat!" />
  <string key="T2010013" eng="The Classic Burst Shotgun gives you the feeling of an medieval shotgun." />
  <string key="T2010014" eng="Hand Gun with a toy gun concept used during childhood." />
  <string key="T2010015" eng="Helps to aim, but it is less accurate at long-distance attacks." />
  <string key="T2010016" eng="This gun works by compressed air, turned into explosions. The energy needs to be chared before the blast. Movement speed is reduced during the charge." />
  <string key="T2010017" eng="Next Generation Sub Machine Gun. Bites their prey badly with sharp teeth." />
  <string key="T2010018" eng="Helps to aim, but it is less accurate at long-distance attacks and rapid shooting. Randomly fires a critical shot." />
  <string key="T2010020" eng="Strong like a diamond, the unique version of the Air Gun." />
  <string key="T2010021" eng="Exocister's main weapon for killing devils. It is recommened to novices. Easy to aim." />
  <string key="T2010022" eng="Helps to aim, but it is less accurate at long-distance attacks and rapid shooting. Randomly fires a critical shot." />
  <string key="T2010023" />
  <string key="T2010024" eng="Fast and Furious to attack the enemy. It has high attack, but low accurate as increased the attack time." />
  <string key="T2010026" eng="Fast and furious Piranha attack! Bullet focus is decreasing during longer attacks." />
  <string key="T2010027" eng="Skull Handgun with a scary skull design" />
  <string key="T2010028" eng="Specially designed dual handguns for the Netsphere. With this weapon, you fight as stylish as in Eastern action flics. {N}By using some of your SP, you can attack your opponent while being in the air or when dodging!" />
  <string key="T2010029" eng="Semi-rifle with Sweet melody, fast as thunder" />
  <string key="T2010030" eng="Rifle strong as thunder" />
  <string key="T2010031" eng="Enhanced Smash Rifle with NetSphere's AI data" />
  <string key="T2010032" eng="The vibrant orange color of this revolver radiates power" />
  <string key="T2010033" eng="Spade shaped Submachine Gun which becomes more powerful in Wonderland" />
  <string key="T2010034" eng="Fight the heat! Cool down yourself and others with this nice water gun. Homing Rifle Unique Watergun" />
  <string key="T2010035" eng="A Smash Rifle that has been originally used by an adventurer in S4. The reflected light from the Smash Rifle helps the adventurers when they explore in the darkness." />
  <string key="T2010038" eng="This gun was created by the legendary Hacker G, but never released. Until now. {N}{CB-255,0,0,255} The Collecting Book effect can be acquired once the Burning Winter Boy/Sexy Winter Girl set is acquired. {N} Buff Effect: No SP guage will be reduced during use of jumping actions." />
  <string key="T2010039" eng="A submachine gun with a cherry blossom pattern. It looks like cherry blossoms might just shoot out of the barrel!" />
  <string key="T2010040" eng="A revolver modeled after a puppy at a cherry blossom festival. Don't be fooled by its cute design. It's much more wicked than it looks!" />
  <string key="T2010041" eng="A new burst Shotgun with some powerful upgrades over the previous model. It sports a larger clip with increased Accuracy while firing. Its look has been completely redesigned." />
  <string key="T2010042" eng="Don't let its fluffy face and sweet demeanor fool you. This little critter packs a scorching laser blast!!" />
  <string key="T2010043" eng="You might be tempted to take a nibble, but beware! This tasty snack packs a scorching laser blast!!" />
  <string key="T2010044" />
  <string key="T2010045" />
  <string key="T2010046" />
  <string key="T2010047" />
  <string key="T2010048" />
  <string key="T2010049" eng="This mafia-style assault rifle is famous among Neden-based leaguers.{N}Upgraded based on data leaked from Dominic's secret project, this weapon is part of the effort to introduce real-world weapons to the Net Sphere for battle simulation." />
  <string key="T2010050" eng="Unique dual magnum combo popular among gangsters in Neden.{N}Available in various colors but the unwritten rule is one should always use two magnums in different colors.{N}The gun in the left hand is called  L'umanità, and its partner in your right hand is L'onore." />
  <string key="T2010051" eng="The Envy Ranger version of the Spark Rifle.{N}The primary weapon of the Envy Rangers,{N}its bursting bullets are the bane of lovebirds everywhere." />
  <string key="T2010052" eng="The Envy Ranger version of the Air Gun.{N}A deadly weapon of the Envy Rangers,{N}its blast is enough to send lovebirds scattering." />
  <string key="T2010053" />
  <string key="T2010054" eng="Are you ready for summer? Then head on down to the beach for some fun in the sun!{N}Don't forget to bring this 2016 version of the Unique Revolver along for the ride! What are you waiting for?!{N}Have a blast this summer with Davy and Nautica!" />
  <string key="T2010055" />
  <string key="T2010056" eng="This powerful demonic weapon pulls its user deeper into damnation each time it is used." />
  <string key="T2010057" eng="Modified version of an assault rifle well-known for its excellent safety. It's been designed to work in its full potential in any type of environment.{N}[Used in Marksmanship Training at Netsphere Highschool]" />
  <string key="T2010058" eng="UMG-11 is a submachine gun for raining that's popular amongst military types. Fast firing speed is its advantage against enemies with low HP." />
  <string key="T2010059" eng="Gold edition of the UMG-11. Its most stunning feature is the bling-bling gold covered exterior." />
  <string key="T2010061" eng="The star of this beautiful weapon is filled with luck!" />
  <string key="T2010062" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2010063" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2010064" eng="This Neon painted gun was created by Lgndz!" />
  <string key="T2010065" eng="An Assault Rifle with strange colors!" />
  <string key="T2010066" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2010067" eng="Dusk will eat you and Dawn will make you shine!" />
  <string key="T2010068" eng="A Smash Rifle colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2010069" eng="A Hand Gun colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2010072" eng="Looks like Miss Fortune dropped her weapons.. Time to kill some smurfs with it." />
  <string key="T2010080" eng="An Assault Rifle colored in a golden shape." />
  <string key="T2020003" eng="Dracula's Electronic guitar frightens you with a melody of blood-red temptation." />
  <string key="T2020004" eng="The battleground gets heated up in red by countless bullets." />
  <string key="T2020005" eng="Multiple targeting Gatling Gun. You can install this weapon for more power attack." />
  <string key="T2020006" eng="Vanish into the shadow. Install this weapon into the ground to have a more powerful weapon." />
  <string key="T2020007" eng="This heavy weapon has been specially designed with this unknown technology{N}and amazingly its weight has been reduced.{N} Firing speed is much faster than the speed of light.{N}It is always aiming for middle of its target." />
  <string key="T2020008" eng="This unique machinegun was secretly imported to China by the group of hackers. It was orginally designed to assasinate agents." />
  <string key="T2020009" eng="S4 League is now back with new type of MK2 weapon - Turret MK2 with better defense rate. A player with Turret MK2 will rule the game." />
  <string key="T2020010" eng="Newly invented weapon by enigmatic hacker group, Mad 'M', of S4 League. Can use for rapid fires and a big strong shot. Also, has various special functions according to the style of Mad 'M'." />
  <string key="T2020011" eng="A Rocket Launcher upgraded by Mad 'M'. It's bigger and comes with more firepower. It uses a two-step compression, allowing for actioned-packed control. It also has lots of special functions, just the way Mad 'M' likes it." />
  <string key="T2020012" eng="Spew out bullets in a V for victory! Use the Light Machine Gun with its two additional muzzles to spray bullets continuously. Deals weak damage over a large area, but critical accuracy will drop dramatically." />
  <string key="T2020039" eng="Newly created Gauss Rifle MK2. Occupy Net Sphere with upgraded Gauss Rifle MK2." />
  <string key="T2020040" eng="Newly created Gauss Rifle MK2. Occupy Net Sphere with upgraded Gauss Rifle MK2." />
  <string key="T2020041" eng="Newly created Gauss Rifle MK2. Occupy Net Sphere with upgraded Gauss Rifle MK2." />
  <string key="T2020042" eng="A unique and powerful Heavy Machine Gun!{N}Three barrels fire consecutively while rotating! It has a high magazine capacity and a wide attack range, but requires extra time to warm up." />
  <string key="T2020043" />
  <string key="T2020044" />
  <string key="T2020045" eng="Whatever area attacked by the Slayer will be effortlessly erased from the map. There's no escaping the hail of bullets when an enemy enters the range of the Slayer." />
  <string key="T2030003" eng="Low-cost, high-efficiency Rail gun tuned to focus on concentrating energy. It has more accurate and stronger attack power." />
  <string key="T2030004" eng="Experience the taste of ade which is fired from Dragonade." />
  <string key="T2030005" />
  <string key="T2030006" eng="Bolt Action Gun weapon that is able to target the enemy from the long distance.  Because of its accuracy, there will be a small movement during the zoom in mode." />
  <string key="T2030007" eng="Unique Mad bunny Railgun stronger than ever!" />
  <string key="T2030008" eng="A gun that has been tuned by Darten, the Hunter. Because of its high sensibility, there will be a small movement during the zoom in mode." />
  <string key="T2030009" eng="Martin's Unique Rail Gun{N}A rail gun hidden in the guise of a simple stick.{N}Its name, Pretender, refers to its subtle, disguised appearance." />
  <string key="T2030010" eng="It's a toy water-gun that shoots water whith striking precision.{N} Users under 18 years of age must be accompanied by an experienced trainer when using this item." />
  <string key="T2030012" eng="There is no description for this item yet." />
  <string key="T2040004" eng="If you look down on it, you might have to pay dearly later on. The sting of the Honey Bee is very painful!" />
  <string key="T2040005" eng="Now Fumbi supports you on the battle ground. Let's rock with Fumbi!" />
  <string key="T2040006" />
  <string key="T2040007" />
  <string key="T2040008" />
  <string key="T2040009" />
  <string key="T2040010" />
  <string key="T2050002" eng="Big energy implosion for a huge blast. Attention: The blast can damage allies nearby!" />
  <string key="T2050003" eng="Fires a special bullet out of concentrated energy and hits with a huge lightning explosion. It damages all players nearby the detonation, even allies!" />
  <string key="T2050004" eng="Throwing weapon for healing multiple players. But, you can't heal yourself." />
  <string key="T2050005" eng="Unique Rescue Gun. Music is the best healing therapy. Let’s DJing!" />
  <string key="T2050006" eng="Skull Patterned Earth Bomber" />
  <string key="T2050007" eng="A newly created bomber that prevents an enemy's movement with strong lightning power. It explodes faster than the previous model, and now it is more effective in limiting enemies' damage and movement." />
  <string key="T2050008" eng="The MK2 Rescue Gun grants stronger healing abilities. A new weapon that allows you to heal and reload simultaneously! Help your allies with the MK2 Rescue Gun!" />
  <string key="T2050009" />
  <string key="T2050010" eng="An unique version of the mine gun!{N}Shake off the heat with star balloons on a summer night!" />
  <string key="T2050011" />
  <string key="T2050012" eng=" A toy made by Dead Pixel modelled after Fumbi.{N}Despite it's toy-like appearance, it detonates very loudly. Handle with caution." />
  <string key="T2050013" eng="Destruction Glitch's Unique Lightning Bomber.{N}Object: This small packet of error codes can even be generated by a stationary Destruction Glitch.{N}A dark fissure tears through space, inflicting internal code disintegration upon those in its path." />
  <string key="T2050014" eng="A bomb shaped liked a watermelon.{N} Don't be fooled by its delicious disguise— this melon's not for eating!" />
  <string key="T2050015" eng="The Earth Bomber wipes out enemies with a rough snow storm." />
  <string key="T2050016" eng="The Earth Bomber wipes out enemies with a rough snow storm." />
  <string key="T2060003" eng="You can feel the mysterious aurora and the warm love from the princess from far far away." />
  <string key="T2060004" eng="The Mind Shock which was infected by Alice Baby. It takes away the HP from opponent players and recovers the own HP." />
  <string key="T2060005" eng="A cube that is used by the magicians to heal league players. It's very powerful." />
  <string key="T2060006" eng="The Envy Ranger version of the Mind Shock.{N}Feel the power of envy!" />
  <string key="T3000003" eng="It's one of passive skills and if you equip it, the item effects are activated. Both HP+20 and SP+20 are increased, so you can easily react against various situations." />
  <string key="T3000006" />
  <string key="T3000007" eng="Both HP and SP increase +5 compared to the previous Dual-Mastery due to the upgrade of the Enhancement and SP Support Systems." />
  <string key="T3000123" eng="It's one of passive skills and if you equip it, the item effects are activated. All Stats are increased to the Force Pack Stats" />
  <string key="T3010002" eng="Give the energy of the hot summer clean up the cool water sports! Anchoring unique type!{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}SP Reduced consumption(-5%),Use distance Increase(+5%)" />
  <string key="T3010003" eng="Be like a dolphin jumping on the surface of the ocean!{N}Could life get any better?!{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Reduces SP consumption (-5%), Increases range (+5%)" />
  <string key="T3020002" eng="Newly enhanced Demon wings! Feel the speed of demon wings and get better position before your enemy. {N}{CB-255,255,0,255}(SP usage -5%, MoveSpeed +10%)" />
  <string key="T3020004" eng="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Virtual Wing.{N}This unique equipment was developed during Luna's test phase.{N}Fashioned after a set of eagle's wings, it was designed to fold for easy storage." />
  <string key="T3050002" eng="Powers' Shield effectively and reliably absorbs enemy bullets, rendering them harmless.Deploys a shield in the front of {N}. Can be used to deflect enemy projectiles and deal damage. Allies behind the shield can provide suppressing fire, which will pass through the shield. However, the shield will disengage upon use of a Melee attack.{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Powers' Shield (Duration increases, SP Consumption decreases when attacked)" />
  <string key="T3050003" />
  <string key="T3050004" />
  <string key="T3060002" eng="Looks like a Toy block but it has enhanced power than it looks.{N}Set the block wall in front of yourself. Use it wisely." />
  <string key="T3060003" eng="Block that is upgraded by The World. Increase the solidity of the Block by using ice crystals. Ice Block {N}{CB-255,255,0,255}(SP Usage (-16%), HP (+7%)" />
  <string key="T3070002" eng="Very delicious sausage! Tie up the enemy with chains. Bounded players cannot move for 3 seconds but able to use skills and attack.{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}SP Reduced consumption(-20%)),Use distance Increase(+20%)" />
  <string key="T3070003" />
  <string key="T3070004" eng="Code: one of Glitch's techniques that destroys the opponent's avatar rights and forcefully takes control.{N}It was once a technique that could control an opponent's movement, but after the Leaguers fought back, is was only sufficient for obstructing movement.{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}SP Reduced consumption(-20%),Use distance Increase(+20%)" />
  <string key="T3080001" eng="Defensive skill bounces off bullets by changing the character’s body to hard steel. The character cannot move while he uses the skill. On Metallic status, a character gets his HP gradually and defensive power increases as well. At the same time, it gives the damage back to the attacker." />
  <string key="T3080002" eng="Defensive skill bounces off bullets by changing the character’s body to hard steel. The character cannot move while he uses the skill. On Metallic status, a character gets his HP gradually and defensive power increases as well. At the same time, it gives the damage back to the attacker. {N}{CB-255,255,0,255}(SP usage -5%, Defense +5%)" />
  <string key="T3080003" eng="This Metallic Fumbi will transform you into a beautifully groomed Fumbi.{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}(SP usage -5%, Defense +5%)" />
  <string key="T3090001" />
  <string key="T3100001" eng="Drains the SP of enemies and also gives them a push." />
  <string key="T3100001" />
  <string key="T3110001" eng="With this skill you are able to dash quickly to the direction you are looking at." />
  <string key="T3110001" />
  <string key="T3120001" />
