  <string key="T4052203" eng="Looks exactly like seaweed, but it's actually made of paper.{N}It's not edible. Don't ask me how I know." />
  <string key="T4052204" eng="This faux fish was picked up with a magnet. {N} I wonder who threw it away..." />
  <string key="T4052205" eng="Marsh and Mallow are both enthralled with this water-breather.{N}I'm not convinced... I guess we'll have to agree to disagree." />
  <string key="T4052206" eng="Delicious! This is the best crab you'll eat all year." />
  <string key="T4052207" eng="This armored reptile glitters with gold and only appears every thousand years.{N}Who can possibly resist its charms?" />
  <string key="T4052208" eng="Calm waters, can change you to a great tsunami!" />
  <string key="T4052209" eng="Contains nutrients that can enhance both you and your equipment!" />
  <string key="T4052210" eng="When the night is dark, you will be a star!" />
  <string key="T4052211" eng="Light up the morning, with your presence!" />
  <string key="T4052212" eng="This box could not even contain the hotness of this summer set!" />
  <string key="T4052213" eng="Peel it and open up the best box of our summer event!" />
