  <string key="T5040006" eng="It guarantees to get a permanent item out of a capsule. {N} The effect will be gone after obtaining 1 permanent Item. {N}{N}{CB-255,0,0,255}This will not work on Skill Capsules {N} Warning: boosted effect will be applied even if the capsule you're using next doesn't contain a permanent item.{N}Random Esperchip Capsule  {N}Normal Weapon Box {N}Normal Costume Box {N}Weapon capsule x1/5/30 {N}Male/Female Costume capsule x1/5/306) Pen package (The one you get when you level up your Character) {N}Any Level Reward Capsule {N}If using the unique booster for Double Capsules, only the first of the two items is given out permanently." />
