  <string key="TIP272" eng="Close range weapon with plasma cracker installed. It deals high damage and allows you to use the sprint ability and stun several enemies with a jump attack." />
  <string key="TIP273" eng="Close range weapon with plasma cracker installed. It deals high damage and allows you to use the sprint ability and stun several enemies with a jump attack." />
  <string key="TIP274" eng="Weapon that increases attack chance by guarding the attack of an enemy using a close range weapon" />
  <string key="TIP275" eng="Tuned close range weapon with the strength of a baseball bat. It features a spin attack for extra damage to nearby opponents." />
  <string key="TIP276" eng="Japan Do' is wrong!. 'Katana' is right" />
  <string key="TIP277" eng="not trans" />
  <string key="TIP278" eng="Suitable weapon for medium distance attacks with rapid fire rate and average accuracy." />
  <string key="TIP279" eng="Suitable weapon for medium distance attacks with rapid fire rate and average accuracy." />
  <string key="TIP28" eng="Monk's face for those who want to become a member of Netsphere's Pirates" />
  <string key="TIP280" eng="This weapon has massive power in close range.{N}It is perfect for attacks against close range opponents{N}because it has a knock back effect. But it is inefficient{N}against long range opponents because of low accuracy." />
  <string key="TIP281" eng="It has a lower fire rate than the Submachine Gun but makes up for this with a much higher accuracy while zoomed in half-way." />
  <string key="TIP282" eng="Supports lots of ammo and close range attacks. Efficient for medium range attacks due to lots of ammo and powerful impact. Also can melee attack close enemies." />
  <string key="TIP283" eng="An easy to use shooting weapon with fast attack speed. When equipped, the character's movement would become faster and quicker." />
  <string key="TIP284" eng="Weapon effective in close range. You can shoot serveral bullets at one time and push opponents and face close range weapons easily." />
  <string key="TIP285" eng="Gatling gun which can attack several enemies. It is useful to guard team players, with a large magazine and wide attack range. But it is difficult to manage in a desperate situation because it has a warm-up time unlike other weapons." />
  <string key="TIP286" eng="Single and automatic burst rifle. The longer you fire the more the accuracy drops. To keep a high accuracy, carefully balance the length of your bursts." />
  <string key="TIP287" eng="Sniping weapon which attacks with high density gravity energy. You have to gather energy for stronger attacks. But your movement speed is decreased while you gather the energy." />
  <string key="TIP288" eng="Weapon that condenses and launches strong energy from a spinning rail inside the weapon. The energy explodes at the target and damages opponents nearby." />
  <string key="TIP289" eng="Installation weapon that finds and attacks an enemy. It only attacks enemies in front of it, and doesn't change to the opponents direction." />
  <string key="TIP29" eng="Mask worn by elite guards{N}of premium sector." />
  <string key="TIP290" eng="Installation weapon which stuns and decreases HP{N}to nearby enemies. Unlike the sentry gun, this weapon also affects all enemies within the 360 degree radius." />
  <string key="TIP291" eng="Installation weapon which stuns and decreases HP to nearby enemies. Unlike the sentry gun, this weapon also affects all enemies within the 360 degree radius." />
  <string key="TIP292" eng="Weapon with compressed explosive energy in ball form for carefully timed sniping. It is made to explode on physical contact. Research into the flight of the ball is essential." />
  <string key="TIP293" eng="Mental weapon that can recover your teams health. It can penetrate through walls or obstacles." />
  <string key="TIP294" eng="Mental weapon that absorbs enemy health by disturbing the mind of the enemy. It causes huge shock damage by penetrating walls or obstacles." />
  <string key="TIP295" eng="A passive skill that will be effective simply by wearing it, you don't need to activate it. This will increase your survival time by increasing your physical strength." />
  <string key="TIP296" eng="A passive skill that will be effective simply by wearing it, you don't need to activate it. This will increase your survival time by increasing your physical strength." />
  <string key="TIP297" eng="A skill that allows you to move quickly by launching a grappling chain at the wall or background. Cannot be used for long distance." />
  <string key="TIP298" eng="A skill that ignores the laws of physics and moves you into the air. When using this skill you will easily conquer high areas by rising quickly. However movement speed in the air is slow." />
  <string key="TIP299" eng="A skill that allows you to hide your appearance. If you stand still you are totally invisible, but if you move you will be detected because objects around you are reflected. If you attack while you are invisible, your original appearance is revealed." />
  <string key="TIP3" eng="Attractive wild style Head." />
