  <string key="TIP300" eng="A skill that allows you to sense an enemy's location in a certain range and send it to team players. You are able to sense an opponent using the Invisible skill." />
  <string key="TIP301" eng="This skill creates a wall in front of you. You can defend using this by blocking a route or making a cover." />
  <string key="TIP302" eng="This skill creates a wall in front of you. You can defend using this by blocking a route or making a cover." />
